data.name: Book the Green Room
data.short_description:
[contact-form]

The green room’s max capacity is 30 people. Reserving the date / time of your event is free. We can also accommodate large groups, with seating for 85 board game players at a time. If you have a large group, let us know and we’ll send you our large group rate.

GROUP RATES

Reserve your event for up to 30 guests for $100.

data.name: Dymo LabelWriter 4XL
data.description:
• Print Extra Large Shipping Labels up to 4” x 6”
  • Select from over 60 professional label templates and customize text and graphics with free DYMO Label Software
  • Compatible with Microsoft Office, Quickbooks, and More
  • Print shipping labels directly from popular online selling platforms such as DYMO Stamps, eBay, Amazon, Etsy, and Iabol
  • Direct thermal printing eliminates the need for costly ink or toner
  • Print USPS-approved DYMO Stamps from your desktop - no monthly fee, contracts, or commitments (US only)
  • System Requirements: Windows 7 or later, Mac OS v10.10 or later
  • Includes: LabelWriter® 4XL printer, adapter, power cable, USB 2.0 cable, Quick Start guide, and starter roll of 4x6 extra large shipping labels
  • For best results use DYMO authentic labels only
  • Bonus: 1 extra roll of labels when you pay with points!
data.short_description:
High Volume Jobs? Not a Problem.

The DYMO LabelWriter 4XL is a wide-format label printer that accommodates the entire line of LabelWriter labels for maximum flexibility, and is also compatible with a variety of popular online selling platforms and shipping carriers. It’s ideal for extra-large shipping and warehouse labels, along with label styles for file folders, name badges, and more. It’s ideal for extra-large shipping and warehouse labels, including 4 inch international shipping labels, along with label styles for file folders, name badges, online postage, mailing and shipping labels, and more.
